</pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="k">using</span> <span class="nn">SpeechLib</span><span class="p">;</span>
</pre></td></tr></tbody></table></code></pre></figure>

<p>Double click on the button we created before - this will create a new method, in which weâ€™ll add the code that converts text to speech:</p>

